snippet.title: Quantum Ruins Trailer | Alpha 2.0
snippet.description:
"Okoro.

They've been waiting for you.

Don't be afraid Okoro,
I will always be by your side.
"

Play the Alpha 2.0 now: https://rics-devlogs.itch.io/quantum-ruins-pre-alpha
Watch me develop the game LIVE on Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/rics_devlogs
Support the game with a Ko-Fi : https://ko-fi.com/ricdevlogs
Discord Server: https://discord.gg/txe3vDf

Quick Facts:
- name:  Riccardo
- age: 26 year old
- where I come from: Italy

- engine used: Godot
